sequenceDiagram
    actor Player
    participant Frontend
    participant Game as JavaScript Game
    participant API as Flask-RESTX API

    Player->>Frontend: Open Play page
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/v1/games
    API-->>Frontend: Return available games
    Frontend-->>Player: Display game cards
    Player->>Frontend: Hover and select a game
    Frontend->>Game: Start selected game
    Game-->>Player: Run gameplay in browser
    Game-->>Frontend: Game ends with final score